                      "stdout": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Services;\n\nuse App\\Models\\Ethesis;\nuse App\\Models\\JournalArticle;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Http;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Log;\n\nclass RepoSyncService\n{\n    protected string $baseUrl = 'https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/cgi/oai2';\n    protected int $timeout = 60;\n\n    public function sync(): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['thesis' => 0, 'article' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n        $url = \"{$this->baseUrl}?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=oai_dc\";\n        $pageCount = 0;\n\n        while ($url) {\n            try {\n                $pageCount++;\n                Log::info(\"Syncing page {$pageCount}...\");\n                \n                $response = Http::retry(3, 2000)->timeout($this->timeout)->get($url);\n                if (!$response->successful()) {\n                    Log::warning(\"HTTP error on page {$pageCount}\", ['status' => $response->status()]);\n                    $stats['errors']++;\n                    // Try to get next page anyway\n                    $url = $this->getNextPageUrl($response->body());\n                    continue;\n                }\n\n                $result = $this->processPage($response->body());\n                $stats['thesis'] += $result['thesis'];\n                $stats['article'] += $result['article'];\n                $stats['skipped'] += $result['skipped'];\n                $stats['errors'] += $result['errors'] ?? 0;\n\n                // Get next page\n                $url = $this->getNextPageUrl($response->body());\n                \n                if ($url) usleep(500000); // 500ms delay\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::error('Repo sync page error', ['page' => $pageCount, 'error' => $e->getMessage()]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n                // Don't break - try to continue if there might be more pages\n                break;\n            }\n        }\n\n        Log::info(\"Sync completed\", ['pages' => $pageCount, 'stats' => $stats]);\n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processPage(string $xml): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['thesis' => 0, 'article' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n        \n        preg_match_all('/<record>(.*?)<\\/record>/s', $xml, $matches);\n        \n        foreach ($matches[1] as $record) {\n            try {\n                $result = $this->processRecord($record);\n                if ($result === 'thesis') $stats['thesis']++;\n                elseif ($result === 'article') $stats['article']++;\n                else $stats['skipped']++;\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::warning('Record process error', ['error' => substr($e->getMessage(), 0, 200)]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processRecord(string $record): ?string\n    {\n        // Extract identifier\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $idMatch);\n        $externalId = $idMatch[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return null;\n\n        // Extract type\n        $types = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:type');\n        $isThesis = in_array('Thesis', $types);\n        $isArticle = in_array('Article', $types) || in_array('PeerReviewed', $types);\n\n        if ($isThesis) {\n            return $this->saveThesis($record, $externalId);\n        } elseif ($isArticle) {\n            return $this->saveArticle($record, $externalId);\n        }\n\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    protected function saveThesis(string $record, string $externalId): ?string\n    {\n        // Skip if exists\n        if (Ethesis::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $title = $this->extract($record, 'dc:title');\n        if (!$title) return null;\n\n        $creators = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:creator');\n        $author = $creators[0] ?? 'Unknown';\n        \n        $abstract = $this->extract($record, 'dc:description');\n        $date = $this->extract($record, 'dc:date');\n        $year = $date ? (int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URL\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $url = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Get PDF URL\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        Ethesis::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'external_url' => $url ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'title' => $title,\n            'author' => $author,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'year' => $year,\n            'type' => 'skripsi', // Default, bisa di-refine\n            'is_public' => true,\n            'file_path' => $pdfUrl,\n        ]);\n\n        return 'thesis';\n    }\n\n    protected function saveArticle(string $record, string $externalId): ?string\n    {\n        // Skip if exists\n        if (JournalArticle::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $title = $this->extract($record, 'dc:title');\n        if (!$title) return null;\n\n        $creators = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:creator');\n        $authors = array_map(fn($c) => ['name' => trim($c)], $creators);\n        \n        $abstract = $this->extract($record, 'dc:description');\n        $date = $this->extract($record, 'dc:date');\n        $year = $date ? (int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URLs\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $repoUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        $ojsUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'ejournal.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Extract journal info from identifier\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $citation = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_contains($i, 'ISSN') || str_contains($i, 'pp.'));\n        \n        $journalName = 'UNIDA Repository';\n        $volume = null;\n        $issue = null;\n        \n        if ($citation && preg_match('/([A-Za-z\\s]+),\\s*(\\d+)\\s*\\((\\d+)\\)/', $citation, $m)) {\n            $journalName = trim($m[1]);\n            $volume = $m[2];\n            $issue = $m[3];\n        }\n\n        // Get PDF URL\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        JournalArticle::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'journal_code' => 'repo',\n            'journal_name' => $journalName,\n            'title' => $title,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'authors' => $authors,\n            'volume' => $volume,\n            'issue' => $issue,\n            'publish_year' => $year,\n            'published_at' => $date,\n            'url' => $ojsUrl ??                     "Text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Services;\n\nuse App\\Models\\Ethesis;\nuse App\\Models\\JournalArticle;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Http;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Log;\n\nclass RepoSyncService\n{\n    protected string $baseUrl = 'https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/cgi/oai2';\n    protected int $timeout = 60;\n\n    public function sync(): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['thesis' => 0, 'article' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n        $url = \"{$this->baseUrl}?verb=ListRecords&metadataPrefix=oai_dc\";\n        $pageCount = 0;\n\n        while ($url) {\n            try {\n                $pageCount++;\n                Log::info(\"Syncing page {$pageCount}...\");\n                \n                $response = Http::retry(3, 2000)->timeout($this->timeout)->get($url);\n                if (!$response->successful()) {\n                    Log::warning(\"HTTP error on page {$pageCount}\", ['status' => $response->status()]);\n                    $stats['errors']++;\n                    // Try to get next page anyway\n                    $url = $this->getNextPageUrl($response->body());\n                    continue;\n                }\n\n                $result = $this->processPage($response->body());\n                $stats['thesis'] += $result['thesis'];\n                $stats['article'] += $result['article'];\n                $stats['skipped'] += $result['skipped'];\n                $stats['errors'] += $result['errors'] ?? 0;\n\n                // Get next page\n                $url = $this->getNextPageUrl($response->body());\n                \n                if ($url) usleep(500000); // 500ms delay\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::error('Repo sync page error', ['page' => $pageCount, 'error' => $e->getMessage()]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n                // Don't break - try to continue if there might be more pages\n                break;\n            }\n        }\n\n        Log::info(\"Sync completed\", ['pages' => $pageCount, 'stats' => $stats]);\n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processPage(string $xml): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['thesis' => 0, 'article' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n        \n        preg_match_all('/<record>(.*?)<\\/record>/s', $xml, $matches);\n        \n        foreach ($matches[1] as $record) {\n            try {\n                $result = $this->processRecord($record);\n                if ($result === 'thesis') $stats['thesis']++;\n                elseif ($result === 'article') $stats['article']++;\n                else $stats['skipped']++;\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::warning('Record process error', ['error' => substr($e->getMessage(), 0, 200)]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processRecord(string $record): ?string\n    {\n        // Extract identifier\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $idMatch);\n        $externalId = $idMatch[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return null;\n\n        // Extract type\n        $types = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:type');\n        $isThesis = in_array('Thesis', $types);\n        $isArticle = in_array('Article', $types) || in_array('PeerReviewed', $types);\n\n        if ($isThesis) {\n            return $this->saveThesis($record, $externalId);\n        } elseif ($isArticle) {\n            return $this->saveArticle($record, $externalId);\n        }\n\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    protected function saveThesis(string $record, string $externalId): ?string\n    {\n        // Skip if exists\n        if (Ethesis::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $title = $this->extract($record, 'dc:title');\n        if (!$title) return null;\n\n        $creators = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:creator');\n        $author = $creators[0] ?? 'Unknown';\n        \n        $abstract = $this->extract($record, 'dc:description');\n        $date = $this->extract($record, 'dc:date');\n        $year = $date ? (int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URL\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $url = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Get PDF URL\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        Ethesis::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'external_url' => $url ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'title' => $title,\n            'author' => $author,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'year' => $year,\n            'type' => 'skripsi', // Default, bisa di-refine\n            'is_public' => true,\n            'file_path' => $pdfUrl,\n        ]);\n\n        return 'thesis';\n    }\n\n    protected function saveArticle(string $record, string $externalId): ?string\n    {\n        // Skip if exists\n        if (JournalArticle::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $title = $this->extract($record, 'dc:title');\n        if (!$title) return null;\n\n        $creators = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:creator');\n        $authors = array_map(fn($c) => ['name' => trim($c)], $creators);\n        \n        $abstract = $this->extract($record, 'dc:description');\n        $date = $this->extract($record, 'dc:date');\n        $year = $date ? (int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URLs\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $repoUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        $ojsUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'ejournal.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Extract journal info from identifier\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $citation = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_contains($i, 'ISSN') || str_contains($i, 'pp.'));\n        \n        $journalName = 'UNIDA Repository';\n        $volume = null;\n        $issue = null;\n        \n        if ($citation && preg_match('/([A-Za-z\\s]+),\\s*(\\d+)\\s*\\((\\d+)\\)/', $citation, $m)) {\n            $journalName = trim($m[1]);\n            $volume = $m[2];\n            $issue = $m[3];\n        }\n\n        // Get PDF URL\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        JournalArticle::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'journal_code' => 'repo',\n            'journal_name' => $journalName,\n            'title' => $title,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'authors' => $authors,\n            'volume' => $volume,\n            'issue' => $issue,\n            'publish_year' => $year,\n            'published_at' => $date,\n            'url' => $ojsUrl ?? $repoUrl ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'pdf_url' => $pdfUrl,\n            'synced_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n\n        return 'article';\n    }\n\n    protected function extract(string $xml, string $tag): ?string\n    {\n        if (preg_match(\"/<{$tag}>([^<]+)<\\/{$tag}>/\", $xml, $match)) {\n            return html_entity_decode(trim($match[1]), ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8');\n        }\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    protected function extractAll(string $xml, string $tag): array\n    {\n        preg_match_all(\"/<{$tag}>([^<]+)<\\/{$tag}>/\", $xml, $matches);\n        return array_map(fn($m) => html_entity_decode(trim($m), ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8'), $matches[1] ?? []);\n    }\n\n    protected function getNextPageUrl(string $xml): ?string\n    {\n        if (preg_match('/<resumptionToken[^>]*>([^<]+)<\\/resumptionToken>/', $xml, $match)) {\n            return \"{$this->baseUrl}?verb=ListRecords&resumptionToken=\" . $match[1];\n        }\n        return null;\n    }\n}"

                "old_str": "    protected function processPage(string $xml): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['thesis' => 0, 'article' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n        \n        preg_match_all('/<record>(.*?)<\\/record>/s', $xml, $matches);\n        \n        foreach ($matches[1] as $record) {\n            try {\n                $result = $this->processRecord($record);\n                if ($result === 'thesis') $stats['thesis']++;\n                elseif ($result === 'article') $stats['article']++;\n                else $stats['skipped']++;\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::warning('Record process error', ['error' => substr($e->getMessage(), 0, 200)]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processRecord(string $record): ?string\n    {\n        // Extract identifier\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $idMatch);\n        $externalId = $idMatch[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return null;\n\n        // Extract type\n        $types = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:type');\n        $isThesis = in_array('Thesis', $types);\n        $isArticle = in_array('Article', $types) || in_array('PeerReviewed', $types);\n\n        if ($isThesis) {\n            return $this->saveThesis($record, $externalId);\n        } elseif ($isArticle) {\n            return $this->saveArticle($record, $externalId);\n        }\n\n        return null;\n    }",
                "new_str": "    protected function processPage(string $xml, string $targetType): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['saved' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n\n        preg_match_all('/<record>(.*?)<\\/record>/s', $xml, $matches);\n\n        foreach ($matches[1] as $record) {\n            try {\n                $saved = $targetType === 'thesis'\n                    ? $this->processThesis($record)\n                    : $this->processArticle($record);\n                $saved ? $stats['saved']++ : $stats['skipped']++;\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::warning('Record error', ['error' => substr($e->getMessage(), 0, 200)]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processThesis(string $record): bool\n    {\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $m);\n        $externalId = $m[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return false;\n\n        if (Ethesis::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        return (bool) $this->saveThesis($record, $externalId);\n    }\n\n    protected function processArticle(string $record): bool\n    {\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $m);\n        $externalId = $m[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return false;\n\n        if (JournalArticle::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        return (bool) $this->saveArticle($record, $externalId);\n    }",

                "new_str": "    protected function processPage(string $xml, string $targetType): array\n    {\n        $stats = ['saved' => 0, 'skipped' => 0, 'errors' => 0];\n\n        preg_match_all('/<record>(.*?)<\\/record>/s', $xml, $matches);\n\n        foreach ($matches[1] as $record) {\n            try {\n                $saved = $targetType === 'thesis'\n                    ? $this->processThesis($record)\n                    : $this->processArticle($record);\n                $saved ? $stats['saved']++ : $stats['skipped']++;\n            } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                Log::warning('Record error', ['error' => substr($e->getMessage(), 0, 200)]);\n                $stats['errors']++;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return $stats;\n    }\n\n    protected function processThesis(string $record): bool\n    {\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $m);\n        $externalId = $m[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return false;\n\n        if (Ethesis::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        return (bool) $this->saveThesis($record, $externalId);\n    }\n\n    protected function processArticle(string $record): bool\n    {\n        preg_match('/<identifier>oai:repo\\.unida\\.gontor\\.ac\\.id:(\\d+)<\\/identifier>/', $record, $m);\n        $externalId = $m[1] ?? null;\n        if (!$externalId) return false;\n\n        if (JournalArticle::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        return (bool) $this->saveArticle($record, $externalId);\n    }",

(int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $repoUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        $ojsUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'ejournal.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with(strtolower($i), '.pdf'));\n\n        JournalArticle::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'journal_code' => 'repo',\n            'journal_name' => 'UNIDA Repository',\n            'title' => $title,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'authors' => $authors,\n            'publish_year' => $year,\n            'published_at' => $date,\n            'url' => $ojsUrl ?? $repoUrl ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'pdf_url' => $pdfUrl,\n            'synced_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n\n        return 'article';\n    }",
                "old_str": "    protected function saveArticle(string $record, string $externalId): ?string\n    {\n        // Skip if exists\n        if (JournalArticle::where('source_type', 'repo')->where('external_id', $externalId)->exists()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        $title = $this->extract($record, 'dc:title');\n        if (!$title) return null;\n\n        $creators = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:creator');\n        $authors = array_map(fn($c) => ['name' => trim($c)], $creators);\n        \n        $abstract = $this->extract($record, 'dc:description');\n        $date = $this->extract($record, 'dc:date');\n        $year = $date ? (int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URLs\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $repoUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        $ojsUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'ejournal.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Extract journal info from identifier\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $citation = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_contains($i, 'ISSN') || str_contains($i, 'pp.'));\n        \n        $journalName = 'UNIDA Repository';\n        $volume = null;\n        $issue = null;\n        \n        if ($citation && preg_match('/([A-Za-z\\s]+),\\s*(\\d+)\\s*\\((\\d+)\\)/', $citation, $m)) {\n            $journalName = trim($m[1]);\n            $volume = $m[2];\n            $issue = $m[3];\n        }\n\n        // Get PDF URL\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        JournalArticle::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'journal_code' => 'repo',\n            'journal_name' => $journalName,\n            'title' => $title,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'authors' => $authors,\n            'volume' => $volume,\n            'issue' => $issue,\n            'publish_year' => $year,\n            'published_at' => $date,\n            'url' => $ojsUrl ?? $repoUrl ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'pdf_url' => $pdfUrl,\n            'synced_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n\n        return 'article';\n    }",

(int) substr($date, 0, 4) : null;\n        \n        // Get URLs\n        $relations = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:relation');\n        $repoUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'repo.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        $ojsUrl = collect($relations)->first(fn($r) => str_contains($r, 'ejournal.unida.gontor.ac.id'));\n        \n        // Extract journal info from identifier\n        $identifiers = $this->extractAll($record, 'dc:identifier');\n        $citation = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_contains($i, 'ISSN') || str_contains($i, 'pp.'));\n        \n        $journalName = 'UNIDA Repository';\n        $volume = null;\n        $issue = null;\n        \n        if ($citation && preg_match('/([A-Za-z\\s]+),\\s*(\\d+)\\s*\\((\\d+)\\)/', $citation, $m)) {\n            $journalName = trim($m[1]);\n            $volume = $m[2];\n            $issue = $m[3];\n        }\n\n        // Get PDF URL\n        $pdfUrl = collect($identifiers)->first(fn($i) => str_ends_with($i, '.pdf'));\n\n        JournalArticle::create([\n            'source_type' => 'repo',\n            'external_id' => $externalId,\n            'journal_code' => 'repo',\n            'journal_name' => $journalName,\n            'title' => $title,\n            'abstract' => $abstract,\n            'authors' => $authors,\n            'volume' => $volume,\n            'issue' => $issue,\n            'publish_year' => $year,\n            'published_at' => $date,\n            'url' => $ojsUrl ?? $repoUrl ?? \"https://repo.unida.gontor.ac.id/{$externalId}/\",\n            'pdf_url' => $pdfUrl,\n            'synced_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n\n        return 'article';\n    }",

                    "Text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Livewire\\Opac\\Journal;\n\nuse App\\Models\\JournalArticle;\nuse App\\Models\\JournalSource;\nuse Livewire\\Component;\nuse Livewire\\WithPagination;\n\nclass JournalIndex extends Component\n{\n    use WithPagination;\n\n    public string $q = '';\n    public string $journal = '';\n    public string $year = '';\n\n    protected $queryString = [\n        'q' => ['except' => ''],\n        'journal' => ['except' => ''],\n        'year' => ['except' => ''],\n    ];\n\n    public function updatingQ()\n    {\n        $this->resetPage();\n    }\n\n    public function updatingJournal()\n    {\n        $this->resetPage();\n    }\n\n    public function updatingYear()\n    {\n        $this->resetPage();\n    }\n\n    public function render()\n    {\n        $sources = JournalSource::where('is_active', true)\n            ->withCount('articles')\n            ->orderBy('name')\n            ->get();\n\n        $query = JournalArticle::query()->with('source');\n\n        if ($this->q) {\n            $search = $this->q;\n            $query->where(function($q) use ($search) {\n                $q->where('title', 'like', \"%{$search}%\")\n                  ->orWhere('abstract', 'like', \"%{$search}%\");\n            });\n        }\n\n        if ($this->journal) {\n            $query->where('journal_code', $this->journal);\n        }\n\n        if ($this->year) {\n            $query->where('publish_year', $this->year);\n        }\n\n        $articles = $query->orderByDesc('published_at')->paginate(20);\n\n        $years = JournalArticle::selectRaw('DISTINCT publish_year')\n            ->whereNotNull('publish_year')\n            ->orderByDesc('publish_year')\n            ->pluck('publish_year');\n\n        return view('livewire.opac.journal.journal-index', [\n            'sources' => $sources,\n            'articles' => $articles,\n            'years' => $years,\n        ])->layout('components.opac.layout', ['title' => 'Jurnal']);\n    }\n}"

          "content": "Pertanyaan bagus! Ini arsitektur offline-first yang modern dan andal untuk sistem perpustakaan:\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ Arsitektur Offline-First untuk Perpustakaan\n\n### **Opsi 1: Progressive Web App (PWA) + IndexedDB**\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      BROWSER (Staff Portal)                  │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Service Worker ──► Cache API (HTML, CSS, JS, Images)       │\n│  IndexedDB ──► Local Data (Katalog, Member, Transaksi)      │\n│  Background Sync ──► Queue offline actions                   │\n└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │ Online? Sync!\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    LARAVEL SERVER (Pusat)                    │\n│  REST API + Sync Endpoints                                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Pro:** Tidak perlu install apapun, works di browser\n**Con:** Storage terbatas (~50MB-1GB), performa kurang untuk data besar\n\n---\n\n### **Opsi 2: Electron + SQLite (Desktop App)** ⭐ RECOMMENDED\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              ELECTRON APP (Desktop - Windows/Mac/Linux)      │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Frontend: Vue/React (reuse existing Livewire logic)        │\n│  Local DB: SQLite (full database replica)                   │\n│  Sync Engine: Bidirectional sync dengan conflict resolution │\n└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │ Online? Sync!\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    LARAVEL SERVER (Pusat)                    │\n│  Sync API: /api/sync/pull, /api/sync/push                   │\n│  Conflict Resolution: Last-write-wins / Manual merge        │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Pro:** Full database offline, performa native, unlimited storage\n**Con:** Perlu install app, maintenance 2 platform\n\n---\n\n### **Opsi 3: Local Server per Cabang** ⭐⭐ MOST RELIABLE\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    KAMPUS CABANG (OPPM, dll)                 │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Mini Server (Raspberry Pi / Mini PC)                       │\n│  └── Laravel Instance (mirror)                              │\n│  └── MySQL/SQLite                                           │\n│  └── Auto-sync saat internet available                      │\n│  Staff Browser ──► http://perpus.local                      │\n└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │ Internet available? Sync!\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    SERVER PUSAT (103.195.19.158)             │\n│  Master Database                                             │\n│  Sync Coordinator                                            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Pro:** Full Laravel, tidak perlu ubah kode, paling reliable\n**Con:** Perlu hardware per cabang, setup lebih kompleks\n\n---\n\n### **Opsi 4: Hybrid PWA + Local API** ⭐⭐⭐ BEST BALANCE\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      STAFF BROWSER                           │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  PWA Shell (cached)                                          │\n│  └── Livewire/Alpine.js UI                                  │\n│  └── Offline Detection                                       │\n│  └── Request Queue (pending actions)                         │\n└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n              ┌────────────┴────────────┐\n              │ Online?                 │ Offline?\n              ▼                         ▼\n┌─────────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────┐\n│   LARAVEL SERVER        │  │   LOCAL COMPANION APP   │\n│   (Normal operation)    │  │   (Electron/Tauri)      │\n│                         │  │   └── SQLite cache      │\n│                         │  │   └── Sync queue        │\n└─────────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Perbandingan Effort & Impact\n\n| Aspek | PWA Only | Electron | Local Server | Hybrid |\n|-------|----------|----------|--------------|--------|\n| **Effort Development** | 🟢 Low | 🟡 Medium | 🟡 Medium | 🟡 Medium |\n| **Perubahan Kode Existing** | 🟢 Minimal | 🟡 Moderate | 🟢 Minimal | 🟢 Minimal |\n| **Reliability Offline** | 🟡 Limited | 🟢 Full | 🟢 Full | 🟢 Full |\n| **Storage Capacity** | 🔴 ~500MB | 🟢 Unlimited | 🟢 Unlimited | 🟢 Unlimited |\n| **Maintenance** | 🟢 Easy | 🟡 Medium | 🔴 Complex | 🟡 Medium |\n| **User Experience** | 🟢 Familiar | 🟡 New app | 🟢 Familiar | 🟢 Familiar |\n| **Cost** | 🟢 $0 | 🟢 $0 | 🟡 ~$50/cabang | 🟢 $0 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Rekomendasi untuk UNIDA\n\n**Untuk kebutuhan Anda (OPPM, cabang tanpa internet stabil), saya rekomendasikan:**\n\n### **Fase 1: PWA + Service Worker** (Effort: 1-2 minggu)\n- Cache halaman staff portal\n- Offline view katalog (read-only)\n- Queue transaksi sirkulasi saat offline\n- Auto-sync saat online\n\n### **Fase 2: Companion Desktop App** (Effort: 2-3 minggu)\n- Electron app dengan SQLite\n- Full offline untuk: Katalog, Member, Sirkulasi\n- Background sync\n- Conflict resolution\n\n---\n\n## 💡 Yang Perlu Diubah di Kode Existing\n\n```\nPerubahan Minimal:\n├── Tambah Service Worker (sw.js)\n├── Tambah upload)\n│   └── GET  /api/sync/status\n├── Tambah updated_at index di tabel utama\n└── Tambah soft deletes tracking\n\nTidak Perlu Diubah:\n├── UI/Views existing\n├── Business logic\n├── Database schema (hanya tambah index)\n└── Authentication flow\n```\n\n---\n\n## ❓ Pertanyaan untuk Menentukan Arsitektur\n\n1. **Berapa cabang** yang butuh offline? // Excel limit\n\n        for ($i = 9; $i <= 508; $i++) {\n            // Row number\n            $sheet->setCellValue('A' . $i, $i - 8);\n            \n            // Bahasa dropdown\n            $validation = $sheet->getCell('I' . $i)->getDataValidation();\n            $validation->setType(DataValidation::TYPE_LIST);\n            $validation->setFormula1('\"Indonesia,Arab,Inggris\"');\n            $validation->setShowDropDown(true);\n\n            // Jumlah eksemplar default\n            $sheet->setCellValue('J' . $i, 1);\n        }\n\n        // Column widths\n        $widths = ['A' => 5, 'B' => 35, 'C' => 25, 'D' => 18, 'E' => 20, 'F' => 8, 'G' => 10, 'H' => 15, 'I' => 12, 'J' => 8, 'K' => 12, 'L' => 20];\n        foreach ($widths as $col => $width) {\n            $sheet->getColumnDimension($col)->setWidth($width);\n        }\n\n        // Freeze header row\n        $sheet->freezePane('A9');\n    }\n\n    protected function createGuideSheet(Spreadsheet $spreadsheet): void\n    {\n        $sheet = $spreadsheet->createSheet();\n        $sheet->setTitle('📖 Panduan');\n\n        $guide = [\n            ['PANDUAN PENGISIAN TEMPLATE IMPORT KOLEKSI', ''],\n            ['', ''],\n            ['1. $sheet->getColumnDimension('B')->setWidth(50);\n    }\n\n    protected function createDdcSheet(Spreadsheet $spreadsheet): void\n    {\n        $sheet = $spreadsheet->createSheet();\n        $sheet->setTitle('🔢 Daftar DDC');\n\n        $sheet->setCellValue('A1', 'Kode DDC');\n        $sheet->setCellValue('B1', 'Klasifikasi');\n        $sheet->setCellValue('C1', 'Contoh Buku');\n        $sheet->getStyle('A1:C1')->getFont()->setBold(true);\n\n        // Get DDC from database\n        $ddcList = DdcClass::orderBy('code')->limit(500)->get();\n        \n        $row = 2;\n        foreach ($ddcList as $ddc) {\n            $sheet->setCellValue('A' . $row, $ddc->code);\n            $sheet->setCellValue('B' . $row, $ddc->name);\n            $row++;\n        }\n\n        // If no DDC in database, add common ones\n        if ($ddcList->isEmpty()) {\n            $commonDdc = [\n                ['000', 'Ilmu Komputer & Informasi'],\n                ['100', 'Filsafat & Psikologi'],\n                ['200', 'Agama'],\n                ['297', 'Islam'],\n                ['297.1', 'Al-Quran & Ilmu Al-Quran'],\n                ['297.2', 'Hadits & Ilmu Hadits'],\n                ['297.4', 'Fiqih Islam'],\n                ['297.5', 'Akhlak & Tasawuf'],\n                ['300', 'Ilmu Sosial'],\n                ['400', 'Bahasa'],\n                ['492.7', 'Bahasa Arab'],\n                ['500', 'Sains'],\n                ['600', 'Teknologi'],\n                ['700', 'Seni & Rekreasi'],\n                ['800', 'Sastra'],\n                ['900', 'Sejarah & Geografi'],\n            ];\n            foreach ($commonDdc as $ddc) {\n                $sheet->setCellValue('A' . $row, $ddc[0]);\n                $sheet->setCellValue('B' . $row, $ddc[1]);\n                $row++;\n            }\n        }\n\n        $sheet->getColumnDimension('A')->setWidth(12);\n        $sheet->getColumnDimension('B')->setWidth(40);\n        $sheet->getColumnDimension('C')->setWidth(30);\n    }\n\n    protected function createCategorySheet(Spreadsheet $spreadsheet): void\n    {\n        $sheet = $spreadsheet->createSheet();\n        $sheet->setTitle('📁 Daftar Kategori');\n\n        $sheet->setCellValue('A1', 'Nama Kategori');\n        $sheet->getStyle('A1')->getFont()->setBold(true);\n\n        $categories = Subject::orderBy('name')->pluck('name');\n        $row = 2;\n        foreach ($categories as $cat) {\n            $sheet->setCellValue('A' . $row++, $cat);\n        }\n\n        $sheet->getColumnDimension('A')->setWidth(40);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Parse uploaded Excel and validate\n     */\n    public function parseAndValidate(ImportBatch $batch, UploadedFile $excel, ?UploadedFile $coversZip = null): array\n    {\n        // Extract covers if provided\n        if ($coversZip) {\n            $this->extractCovers($batch, $coversZip);\n        }\n\n        // Parse Excel\n        $spreadsheet = IOFactory::load($excel->getPathname());\n        $sheet = $spreadsheet->getActiveSheet();\n        $rows = $sheet->toArray(null, true, true, true);\n\n        $preview = [];\n        $stats = ['total' => 0, 'valid' => 0, 'warning' => 0, 'error' => 0];\n\n        // Find header row (contains \"Judul\")\n        $headerRow = 8;\n        $dataStartRow = 9;\n\n        foreach ($rows as $rowNum => $row) {\n            if ($rowNum < $dataStartRow) continue;\n            \n            // Skip empty rows\n            if (empty(trim($row['B'] ?? ''))) continue;\n\n            $stats['total']++;\n            $rowData = $this->parseRow($row, $batch);\n            \n            if ($rowData['status'] === 'error') {\n                $stats['error']++;\n            } elseif ($rowData['status'] === 'warning') {\n                $stats['warning']++;\n            } else {\n                $stats['valid']++;\n            }\n\n            $preview[] = $rowData;\n        }\n\n        // Update batch\n        $batch->update([\n            'total_rows' => $stats['total'],\n            'success_count' => $stats['valid'],\n            'warning_count' => $stats['warning'],\n            'error_count' => $stats['error'],\n            'preview_data' => $preview,\n            'status' => 'ready',\n        ]);\n\n        return [\n            'stats' => $stats,\n            'preview' => $preview,\n        ];\n    }\n\n    protected function parseRow(array $row, ImportBatch $batch): array\n    {\n        $errors = [];\n        $warnings = [];\n\n        $title = trim($row['B'] ?? '');\n        $authors = trim($row['C'] ?? '');\n        $isbn = trim($row['D'] ?? '');\n        $publisher = trim($row['E'] ?? '');\n        $year = trim($row['F'] ?? '');\n        $ddc = trim($row['G'] ?? '');\n        $category = trim($row['H'] ?? '');\n        $language = trim($row['I'] ?? '');\n        $quantity = (int) ($row['J'] ?? 1);\n        $location = trim($row['K'] ?? '');\n        $coverFile = trim($row['L'] ?? '');\n\n        // Validations\n        if (empty($title)) {\n            $errors[] = 'Judul wajib diisi';\n        }\n        if (empty($authors)) {\n            $errors[] = 'Penulis wajib diisi';\n        }\n        if ($quantity < 1) {\n            $errors[] = 'Jumlah eksemplar minimal 1';\n        }\n\n        // DDC validation\n        $ddcResolved = null;\n        $callNumber = null;\n        if (empty($ddc)) {\n            $warnings[] = 'DDC kosong, call number tidak bisa digenerate';\n        } else {\n            $ddcResolved = DdcClass::where('code', $ddc)->first();\n            if (!$ddcResolved) {\n                $warnings[] = \"DDC '$ddc' tidak ditemukan di database\";\n            } else {\n                // Generate call number preview\n                $authorCode = $this->generateAuthorCode($authors);\n                $titleCode = strtolower(substr(preg_replace('/^(the|a|an)\\s+/i', '', $title), 0, 1));\n                $callNumber = \"{$ddc} {$authorCode} {$titleCode}\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Cover validation\n        $coverFound = false;\n        $coverPath = null;\n        if (!empty($coverFile)) {\n            $coverPath = $this->findCoverFile($batch, $coverFile);\n            if ($coverPath) {\n                $coverFound = true;\n            } else {\n                $warnings[] = \"Cover '$coverFile' tidak ditemukan dalam ZIP\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        // ISBN duplicate check\n        if (!empty($isbn)) {\n            $existing = Book::where('isbn', $isbn)->first();\n            if ($existing) {\n                $warnings[] = \"ISBN sudah ada: {$existing->title}\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Language mapping\n        $langMap = ['indonesia' => 'id', 'arab' => 'ar', 'inggris' => 'en'];\n        $langCode = $langMap[strtolower($language)] ?? 'id';\n\n        $status = 'valid';\n        if (!empty($errors)) {\n            $status = 'error';\n        } elseif (!empty($warnings)) {\n            $status = 'warning';\n        }\n\n        return [\n            'status' => $status,\n            'errors' => $errors,\n            'warnings' => $warnings,\n            'data' => [\n                'title' => $title,\n                'authors' => $authors,\n                'isbn' => $isbn,\n                'publisher' => $publisher,\n                'year' => $year ?: null,\n                'ddc' => $ddc,\n                'ddc_name' => $ddcResolved?->name,\n                'call_number' => $callNumber,\n                'category' => $category,\n                'language' => $langCode,\n                'quantity' => $quantity,\n                'location' => $location,\n                'cover_file' => $coverFile,\n                'cover_found' => $coverFound,\n                'cover_path' => $coverPath,\n            ],\n        ];\n    }\n\n    protected function generateAuthorCode(string $authors): string\n    {\n        $firstAuthor = explode(';', $authors)[0];\n        $parts = preg_split('/\\s+/', trim($firstAuthor));\n        $lastName = end($parts);\n        return strtoupper(substr($lastName, 0, 3));\n    }\n\n    protected function extractCovers(ImportBatch $batch, UploadedFile $zip): void\n    {\n        $extractPath = storage_path(\"app/imports/{$batch->id}/covers\");\n        \n        if (!is_dir($extractPath)) {\n            mkdir($extractPath, 0755, true);\n        }\n\n        $zipArchive = new ZipArchive();\n        if ($zipArchive->open($zip->getPathname()) === true) {\n            $zipArchive->extractTo($extractPath);\n            $zipArchive->close();\n        }\n\n        // Index all image files\n        $this->coverFiles = [];\n        $this->indexCovers($extractPath);\n\n        $batch->update(['covers_file' => $zip->getClientOriginalName()]);\n    }\n\n    protected function indexCovers(string $path): void\n    {\n        $files = scandir($path);\n        foreach ($files as $file) {\n            if ($file === '.' || $file === '..') continue;\n            \n            $fullPath = $path . '/' . $file;\n            if (is_dir($fullPath)) {\n                $this->indexCovers($fullPath);\n            } elseif (preg_match('/\\.(jpg|jpeg|png|webp)$/i', $file)) {\n                $this->coverFiles[strtolower($file)] = $fullPath;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    protected function findCoverFile(ImportBatch $batch, string $filename): ?string\n    {\n        // Check indexed files\n        $key = strtolower($filename);\n        if (isset($this->coverFiles[$key])) {\n            return $this->coverFiles[$key];\n        }\n\n        // Try to find in extract directory\n        $basePath = storage_path(\"app/imports/{$batch->id}/covers\");\n        $possiblePaths = [\n            $basePath . '/' . $filename,\n            $basePath . '/covers/' . $filename,\n        ];\n\n        foreach ($possiblePaths as $path) {\n            if (file_exists($path)) {\n                return $path;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Execute import\n     */\n    public function executeImport(ImportBatch $batch, bool $includeWarnings = false): array\n    {\n        $batch->update(['status' => 'processing']);\n        \n        $preview = $batch->preview_data ?? [];\n        $imported = 0;\n        $skipped = 0;\n        $errors = [];\n\n        DB::beginTransaction();\n        try {\n            foreach ($preview as $index => $row) {\n                if ($row['status'] === 'error') {\n                    $skipped++;\n                    continue;\n                }\n\n                if ($row['status'] === 'warning' && !$includeWarnings) {\n                    $skipped++;\n                    continue;\n                }\n\n                try {\n                    $this->importBook($row['data'], $batch);\n                    $imported++;\n                } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n                    $errors[] = \"Baris \" . ($index + 1) . \": \" . $e->getMessage();\n                    $skipped++;\n                }\n            }\n\n            DB::commit();\n\n            $batch->update([\n                'status' => 'completed',\n                'success_count' => $imported,\n                'error_log' => $errors,\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            return [\n                'success' => true,\n                'imported' => $imported,\n                'skipped' => $skipped,\n                'errors' => $errors,\n            ];\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            DB::rollBack();\n            \n            $batch->update([\n                'status' => 'failed',\n                'error_log' => [$e->getMessage()],\n            ]);\n\n            return [\n                'success' => false,\n                'error' => $e->getMessage(),\n            ];\n        }\n    }\n\n    protected function importBook(array $data, ImportBatch $batch): Book\n    {\n        // Find or create publisher\n        $publisher = null;\n        if (!empty($data['publisher'])) {\n            $publisher = Publisher::firstOrCreate(\n                ['name' => $data['publisher']],\n                ['slug' => Str::slug($data['publisher'])]\n            );\n        }\n\n        // Find or create authors\n        $authorIds = [];\n        if (!empty($data['authors'])) {\n            $authorNames = array_map('trim', explode(';', $data['authors']));\n            foreach ($authorNames as $name) {\n                $author = Author::firstOrCreate(\n                    ['name' => $name],\n                    ['slug' => Str::slug($name)]\n                );\n                $authorIds[] = $author->id;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Handle cover\n        $coverPath = null;\n        if (!empty($data['cover_path']) && file_exists($data['cover_path'])) {\n            $ext = pathinfo($data['cover_path'], PATHINFO_EXTENSION);\n            $newName = 'covers/' . Str::uuid() . '.' . $ext;\n            Storage::disk('public')->put($newName, file_get_contents($data['cover_path']));\n            $coverPath = $newName;\n        }\n\n        // Create book\n        $book = Book::create([\n            'branch_id' => $batch->branch_id,\n            'title' => $data['title'],\n            'isbn' => $data['isbn'] ?: null,\n            'publisher_id' => $publisher?->id,\n            'publish_year' => $data['year'],\n            'call_number' => $data['call_number'],\n            'ddc_code' => $data['ddc'],\n            'language' => $data['language'],\n            'cover' => $coverPath,\n            'is_opac_visible' => true,\n        ]);\n\n        // Attach authors\n        if (!empty($authorIds)) {\n            $book->authors()->attach($authorIds);\n        }\n\n        // Attach subject/category\n        if (!empty($data['category'])) {\n            $subject = Subject::where('name', $data['category'])->first();\n            if ($subject) {\n                $book->subjects()->attach($subject->id);\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Create book items (eksemplar)\n        $collectionType = CollectionType::first();\n        for ($i = 1; $i <= $data['quantity']; $i++) {\n            BookItem::create([\n                'book_id' => $book->id,\n                'branch_id' => $batch->branch_id,\n                'collection_type_id' => $collectionType?->id,\n                'barcode' => $this->generateBarcode($book, $i),\n                'shelf_location' => $data['location'],\n                'status' => 'available',\n            ]);\n        }\n\n        return $book;\n    }\n\n    protected function generateBarcode(Book $book, int $copy): string\n    {\n        return sprintf('%s-%04d-%02d', date('Ymd'), $book->id, $copy);\n    }\n}\n",

                "file_text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Livewire\\Staff\\Catalog;\n\nuse App\\Models\\Branch;\nuse App\\Models\\ImportBatch;\nuse App\\Services\\BookImportService;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Auth;\nuse Livewire\\Component;\nuse Livewire\\WithFileUploads;\n\nclass BookImport extends Component\n{\n    use WithFileUploads;\n\n    public $excelFile;\n    public $coversZip;\n    public $branchId;\n    \n    public ?ImportBatch $batch = null;\n    public array $preview = [];\n    public array $stats = [];\n    \n    public string $filterStatus = 'all';\n    public string $search = '';\n    public bool $includeWarnings = true;\n    \n    public bool $showDetailModal = false;\n    public ?array $selectedRow = null;\n\n    protected $rules = [\n        'excelFile' => 'required|file|mimes:xlsx,xls|max:10240',\n        'coversZip' => 'nullable|file|mimes:zip|max:102400',\n        'branchId' => 'required|exists:branches,id',\n    ];\n\n    public function mount()\n    {\n        $user = Auth::user();\n        $this->branchId = $user->branch_id ?? Branch::first()?->id;\n    }\n\n    public function downloadTemplate()\n    {\n        $branch = Branch::findOrFail($this->branchId);\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $path = $service->generateTemplate($branch);\n        \n        return response()->download($path)->deleteFileAfterSend();\n    }\n\n    public function upload()\n    {\n        $this->validate();\n\n        $user = Auth::user();\n        \n        // Create batch\n        $this->batch = ImportBatch::create([\n            'branch_id' => $this->branchId,\n            'user_id' => $user->id,\n            'type' => 'books',\n            'filename' => $this->excelFile->getClientOriginalName(),\n            'status' => 'validating',\n        ]);\n\n        // Parse and validate\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $result = $service->parseAndValidate(\n            $this->batch,\n            $this->excelFile,\n            $this->coversZip\n        );\n\n        $this->stats = $result['stats'];\n        $this->preview = $result['preview'];\n\n        $this->dispatch('upload-complete');\n    }\n\n    public function executeImport()\n    {\n        if (!$this->batch) return;\n\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $result = $service->executeImport($this->batch, $this->includeWarnings);\n\n        if ($result['success']) {\n            session()->flash('success', \"Berhasil import {$result['imported']} buku. {$result['skipped']} dilewati.\");\n            return redirect()->route('staff.catalog.index');\n        } else {\n            session()->flash('error', 'Import gagal: ' . $result['error']);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function cancelImport()\n    {\n        if ($this->batch) {\n            $this->batch->delete();\n        }\n        \n        $this->reset(['batch', 'preview', 'stats', 'excelFile', 'coversZip']);\n    }\n\n    public function showDetail(int $index)\n    {\n        $this->selectedRow = $this->preview[$index] ?? null;\n        $this->showDetailModal = true;\n    }\n\n    public function getFilteredPreviewProperty(): array\n    {\n        $filtered = $this->preview;\n\n        if ($this->filterStatus !== 'all') {\n            $filtered = array_filter($filtered, fn($row) => $row['status'] === $this->filterStatus);\n        }\n\n        if ($this->search) {\n            $search = strtolower($this->search);\n            $filtered = array_filter($filtered, fn($row) => \n                str_contains(strtolower($row['data']['title'] ?? ''), $search) ||\n                str_contains(strtolower($row['data']['authors'] ?? ''), $search)\n            );\n        }\n\n        return array_values($filtered);\n    }\n\n    public function getBranchesProperty()\n    {\n        return Branch::where('is_active', true)->orderBy('name')->get();\n    }\n\n    public function render()\n    {\n        return view('livewire.staff.catalog.book-import', [\n            'filteredPreview' => $this->filteredPreview,\n            'branches' => $this->branches,\n        ]);\n    }\n}\n",

                "file_text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Livewire\\Staff\\Catalog;\n\nuse App\\Models\\Branch;\nuse App\\Models\\ImportBatch;\nuse App\\Services\\BookImportService;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Auth;\nuse Livewire\\Component;\nuse Livewire\\WithFileUploads;\n\nclass BookImport extends Component\n{\n    use WithFileUploads;\n\n    public $excelFile;\n    public $coversZip;\n    public $branchId;\n    \n    public ?ImportBatch $batch = null;\n    public array $preview = [];\n    public array $stats = [];\n    \n    public string $filterStatus = 'all';\n    public string $search = '';\n    public bool $includeWarnings = true;\n    \n    public bool $showDetailModal = false;\n    public ?array $selectedRow = null;\n\n    protected $rules = [\n        'excelFile' => 'required|file|mimes:xlsx,xls|max:10240',\n        'coversZip' => 'nullable|file|mimes:zip|max:102400',\n        'branchId' => 'required|exists:branches,id',\n    ];\n\n    public function mount()\n    {\n        $user = Auth::user();\n        $this->branchId = $user->branch_id ?? Branch::first()?->id;\n    }\n\n    public function downloadTemplate()\n    {\n        $branch = Branch::findOrFail($this->branchId);\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $path = $service->generateTemplate($branch);\n        \n        return response()->download($path)->deleteFileAfterSend();\n    }\n\n    public function upload()\n    {\n        $this->validate();\n\n        $user = Auth::user();\n        \n        // Create batch\n        $this->batch = ImportBatch::create([\n            'branch_id' => $this->branchId,\n            'user_id' => $user->id,\n            'type' => 'books',\n            'filename' => $this->excelFile->getClientOriginalName(),\n            'status' => 'validating',\n        ]);\n\n        // Parse and validate\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $result = $service->parseAndValidate(\n            $this->batch,\n            $this->excelFile,\n            $this->coversZip\n        );\n\n        $this->stats = $result['stats'];\n        $this->preview = $result['preview'];\n\n        $this->dispatch('upload-complete');\n    }\n\n    public function executeImport()\n    {\n        if (!$this->batch) return;\n\n        $service = app(BookImportService::class);\n        $result = $service->executeImport($this->batch, $this->includeWarnings);\n\n        if ($result['success']) {\n            session()->flash('success', \"Berhasil import {$result['imported']} buku. {$result['skipped']} dilewati.\");\n            return redirect()->route('staff.catalog.index');\n        } else {\n            session()->flash('error', 'Import gagal: ' . $result['error']);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function cancelImport()\n    {\n        if ($this->batch) {\n            $this->batch->delete();\n        }\n        \n        $this->reset(['batch', 'preview', 'stats', 'excelFile', 'coversZip']);\n    }\n\n    public function showDetail(int $index)\n    {\n        $this->selectedRow = $this->preview[$index] ?? null;\n        $this->showDetailModal = true;\n    }\n\n    public function getFilteredPreviewProperty(): array\n    {\n        $filtered = $this->preview;\n\n        if ($this->filterStatus !== 'all') {\n            $filtered = array_filter($filtered, fn($row) => $row['status'] === $this->filterStatus);\n        }\n\n        if ($this->search) {\n            $search = strtolower($this->search);\n            $filtered = array_filter($filtered, fn($row) => \n                str_contains(strtolower($row['data']['title'] ?? ''), $search) ||\n                str_contains(strtolower($row['data']['authors'] ?? ''), $search)\n            );\n        }\n\n        return array_values($filtered);\n    }\n\n    public function getBranchesProperty()\n    {\n        return Branch::where('is_active', true)->orderBy('name')->get();\n    }\n\n    public function render()\n    {\n        return view('livewire.staff.catalog.book-import', [\n            'filteredPreview' => $this->filteredPreview,\n            'branches' => $this->branches,\n        ]);\n    }\n}\n",

    "`ga_enabled` sudah diaktifkan, tapi **`ga_measurement_id` masih kosong**. \n\nAnda perlu memasukkan Measurement ID dari Google Analytics. Formatnya seperti `G-XXXXXXXXXX`. Dapatkan dari:\n1. Buka Google Analytics → Admin → Data Streams → pilih stream → copy Measurement ID\n\nSetelah dapat ID-nya, masukkan via:\n- **Filament Admin** → Settings → Analytics → isi Measurement ID\n- Atau beritahu saya ID-nya dan saya update langsung di database\n\nTanpa Measurement ID, script Google Analytics tidak akan dimuat karena kondisi di layout:\n```php\n@if($gaEnabled && $gaMeasurementId)  // <- ga_measurement_id kosong = false\n```\n[Tool uses: none]",
    "> Service Account JSON (Ini dapatnya dmna?)",
    "Service Account JSON didapat dari Google Cloud Console. Berikut langkahnya:\n\n## Cara Mendapatkan Service Account JSON\n\n1. **Buka Google Cloud Console**\n   - https://console.cloud.google.com\n\n2. **Pilih/Buat Project**\n   - Pilih project yang sama dengan Google Analytics Anda\n\n3. **Buat Service Account**\n   - Menu → **IAM & Admin** → **Service Accounts**\n   - Klik **+ CREATE SERVICE ACCOUNT**\n   - Isi nama (misal: `analytics-reader`)\n   - Klik **CREATE AND CONTINUE**\n   - Skip role (tidak perlu)\n   - Klik **DONE**\n\n4. **Generate JSON Key**\n   - Klik service account yang baru dibuat\n   - Tab **KEYS** → **ADD KEY** → **Create new key**\n   - Pilih **JSON** → **CREATE**\n   - File JSON akan terdownload otomatis\n\n5. **Hubungkan ke Google Analytics**\n   - Buka **Google Analytics** → **Admin**\n   - **Property Settings** → **Property Access Management**\n   - Klik **+** → **Add users**\n   - Masukkan email service account (format: `nama@project-id.iam.gserviceaccount.com`)\n   - Beri role **Viewer**\n   - Save\n\n6. **Dapatkan Property ID**\n   - Di Google Analytics → **Admin** → **Property Settings**\n   - Copy **Property ID** (angka, bukan Measurement ID)\n\n---\n\n**Catatan:** Service Account JSON hanya diperlukan jika Anda ingin menampilkan **statistik analytics di dashboard admin** (visitor count, page views, dll). \n\nJika hanya ingin **tracking pengunjung** di website, cukup isi:\n- ✅ `ga_measurement_id` (G-XXXXXXXXXX)\n- ✅ `ga_enabled` = 1\n\nService Account JSON opsional untuk fitur lanjutan.\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "> www data itu user juga kh?",
    "Ya, `www-data` adalah system user yang dibuat otomatis saat install Nginx/Apache.\n\n**Perbedaan:**\n\n| | www-data | vm-4 |\n|---|---|---|\n| Tipe | System user | Regular user |\n| Login | Tidak bisa login SSH | Bisa login SSH |\n| Home | `/var/www` | `/home/vm-4` |\n| Tujuan | Menjalankan web server | User manusia |\n| Shell | `/usr/sbin/nologin` | `/bin/bash` |\n\n**Kenapa ada www-data?**\n- Security: Jika web server di-hack, attacker hanya dapat akses terbatas (bukan root)\n- Isolasi: Proses web terpisah dari user lain\n\n**Saat ini:**\n- Nginx → jalan sebagai www-data\n- PHP-FPM → jalan sebagai www-data\n- Files → mix owner (vm-4 dan www-data)\n\n**Opsi 2 akan ubah:**\n- PHP-FPM → jalan sebagai vm-4\n- Files → semua owned vm-4\n- Nginx → tetap www-data (hanya baca file, tidak perlu write)\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "> Oke sekarng kita review unggah tugas akhir sebelumnya kita ada tahap watermark file, namun sekrn ini proses itu seperti menambah alur, apakah bisa file ang di uploadoleh mahasiswa otomatis terwatermak didalamsistem unggah mandiri tugas akhir? berikan perancangan saja apakah saya perlu share gambar waterk logo unida gontor atau bagaimana berikan gambarran dan arsitektur nya.",
    "## Perancangan Auto-Watermark Unggah Tugas Akhir\n\n### Alur Saat Ini vs Usulan\n\n```\nSAAT INI (Manual):\nMahasiswa Upload → Staff Review → Staff Watermark Manual → Approve → Publish\n\nUSULAN (Auto):\nMahasiswa Upload → Auto Watermark (Background Job) → Staff Review → Approve → Publish\n```\n\n### Arsitektur Teknis\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    UNGGAH TUGAS AKHIR                           │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  1. Mahasiswa Upload PDF                                        │\n│           │                                                     │\n│           ▼                                                     │\n│  2. Store Original File                                         │\n│      storage/app/etheses/original/{id}.pdf                      │\n│           │                                                     │\n│           ▼                                                     │\n│  3. Dispatch Job: WatermarkPdfJob                               │\n│           │                                                     │\n│           ▼                                                     │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐                     │\n│  │  QUEUE WORKER (Background)             │                     │\n│  │                                        │                     │\n│  │  - Load PDF dengan FPDI/TCPDF          │                     │\n│  │  - Tambah watermark setiap halaman:    │                     │\n│  │    • Logo UNIDA (pojok/tengah)         │                     │\n│  │    • Teks: \"Perpustakaan UNIDA Gontor\" │                     │\n│  │    • Opacity: 20-30%                   │                     │\n│  │  - Save ke: etheses/watermarked/       │                     │\n│  │  - Update DB: watermarked_at           │                     │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────┘                     │\n│           │                                                     │\n│           ▼                                                     │\n│  4. Staff Review (File sudah ter-watermark)                     │\n│           │                                                     │\n│           ▼                                                     │\n│  5. Approve → Publish ke EPrints                                │\n│                                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Storage Structure\n\n```\nstorage/app/etheses/\n├── original/          # File asli dari mahasiswa (backup)\n│   └── {id}.pdf\n└── watermarked/       # File yang sudah di-watermark (untuk publish)\n    └── {id}.pdf\n```\n\n### Watermark Options\n\n**Option A: Logo Only**\n- Logo UNIDA Gontor transparan di tengah/pojok setiap halaman\n\n**Option B: Logo + Text**\n- Logo UNIDA + teks \"Perpustakaan UNIDA Gontor\" + tahun\n\n**Option C: Diagonal Text**\n- Teks diagonal \"PERPUSTAKAAN UNIDA GONTOR\" berulang (seperti watermark dokumen resmi)\n\n### Yang Dibutuhkan\n\n1. **Logo UNIDA Gontor** - format PNG dengan background transparan, resolusi tinggi (minimal 500x500px)\n\n2. **Keputusan posisi watermark:**\n   - Tengah halaman (semi-transparan)?\n   - Pojok kanan bawah?\n   - Header/footer setiap halaman?\n\n3. **Opacity level** - biasanya 15-30% agar tidak mengganggu baca\n\n### Dependencies\n\n```bash\n# PHP Library untuk PDF manipulation\ncomposer require setasign/fpdi\ncomposer require tecnickcom/tcpdf\n# atau\ncomposer require spatie/pdf-to-image  # jika perlu convert\n```\n\n---\n\nSilakan share logo UNIDA Gontor (PNG transparan) dan tentukan:\n1. Posisi watermark yang diinginkan\n2. Apakah perlu tambahan teks atau logo saja?\n3. Level transparansi (saran: 20-25%)\n\nSetelah itu saya bisa langsung implementasi job-nya.\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "Implementasi auto-watermark sudah selesai di-deploy ke production.\n\n## Summary Implementasi Auto-Watermark\n\n### Alur Kerja Baru:\n```\nMahasiswa Upload PDF → File Disimpan → WatermarkPdfJob Dispatch → \nQueue Worker Proses → Logo + Text Ditambahkan → File Ter-watermark\n```\n\n### File yang Dibuat/Dimodifikasi:\n\n1. **`app/Jobs/WatermarkPdfJob.php`** (Baru)\n   - Job untuk memproses watermark PDF secara background\n   - Menggunakan FPDI-TCPDF untuk manipulasi PDF\n   - Logo UNIDA 70% di tengah halaman dengan opacity 15%\n   - Teks \"Perpustakaan UNIDA Gontor\" di pojok kanan bawah\n\n2. **`app/Livewire/ThesisSubmissionForm.php`** (Dimodifikasi)\n   - Dispatch `WatermarkPdfJob` setelah file preview/fulltext di-upload\n\n### Dependencies:\n- `setasign/fpdi-tcpdf` - untuk manipulasi PDF dengan transparency support\n\n### Watermark Specs:\n- **Logo**: 70% lebar halaman, di tengah, opacity 15%\n- **Teks**: \"Perpustakaan UNIDA Gontor\" di pojok kanan bawah, font 8pt, opacity 50%\n- **File yang di-watermark**: preview (BAB 1-3) dan fulltext\n\n### Catatan:\n- Watermark diproses secara asynchronous via queue worker\n- File original di-backup dengan suffix `_original.pdf`\n- Logo sudah di-upload ke `/var/www/perpustakaan-app/shared/storage/app/public/logo-unida.png`\n\nSekarang setiap kali mahasiswa upload file PDF tugas akhir, file tersebut akan otomatis ter-watermark dengan logo UNIDA Gontor dan teks perpustakaan.\n[Tool uses: none]",

atau scan QR code               │    │   │\n│  │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘    │   │\n│  │                                                  │   │\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐                                │   │\n│  │  │   📷 Foto   │  Nama: Ahmad Fauzi            │   │\n│  │  │   Member    │  NIM: 2024001                 │   │\n│  │  │             │  Prodi: Teknik Informatika    │   │\n│  │  └─────────────┘  Status: ✅ Aktif             │   │\n│  │                                                  │   │\n│  │        [ ✓ KONFIRMASI KUNJUNGAN ]               │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📐 Database Schema\n\n```\nvisits\n├── id\n├── member_id (FK → members)\n├── branch_id (FK → branches)\n├── visited_at (timestamp)\n├── purpose (enum: baca, pinjam, belajar, lainnya) - optional\n├── device_id (untuk tracking kiosk mana)\n└── created_at\n\nIndexes:\n- (branch_id, visited_at) → untuk statistik per cabang\n- (member_id, visited_at) → untuk history member\n- (visited_at) → untuk laporan harian\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 Flow Detail\n\n```\n1. INPUT\n   ├── Ketik NIM: \"2024001\" \n   │   └── Query: members WHERE member_id = '2024001'\n   │\n   └── Scan QR: Contains member_id\n       └── Same query\n\n2. VALIDASI\n   ├── Member tidak ditemukan → \"NIM tidak terdaftar\"\n   ├── Member expired → \"Keanggotaan sudah habis\"\n   ├── Member suspended → \"Akun diblokir\"\n   └── Member aktif → Lanjut\n\n3. KONFIRMASI\n   └── Tampilkan foto + nama → Member klik konfirmasi\n       (Mencegah salah input)\n\n4. RECORD\n   └── Insert ke tabel visits\n       └── Tampilkan \"Selamat datang, Ahmad!\"\n\n5. ANTI-DUPLICATE\n   └── Cek: sudah visit hari ini?\n       ├── Ya → Update visited_at (perpanjang)\n       └── Tidak → Insert baru\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📱 Implementasi\n\n**1. Public Kiosk Page** (tanpa login)\n```\nRoute: /kiosk/{branch_code}\nContoh: /kiosk/pusat, /kiosk/putri\n```\n\n**2. Staff Dashboard**\n```\n- Lihat visitor hari ini (realtime)\n- Export laporan\n- Manual input (fallback)\n```\n\n**3. Statistics Integration**\n```\n- Tambah ke halaman statistik existing\n- Chart pengunjung per jam/hari/bulan\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔐 Security\n\n1. **Kiosk Mode**: URL khusus per cabang, tidak perlu login\n2. **Rate Limiting**: Max 1 visit per member per 30 menit\n3. **Device Binding**: Optional - kiosk hanya dari IP tertentu\n4. **No Sensitive Data**: Kiosk hanya tampilkan nama + foto, bukan data lengkap\n\n---\n\n### 📈 Statistik yang Bisa Dihasilkan\n\n- Pengunjung per hari/minggu/bulan\n- Jam sibuk (peak hours)\n- Perbandingan antar cabang\n- Member paling aktif berkunjung\n- Tren kunjungan (naik/turun)\n- Rata-rata kunjungan per member\n\n---\n\n### ❓ Pertanyaan untuk Anda\n\n1. **Purpose/Tujuan kunjungan** - Perlu dicatat atau tidak? Google Login (`SocialAuthController.php`)\n- Cek `Member::where('email', $googleUser->getEmail())` - jika ketemu, langsung link\n- Jika tidak ketemu, buat member baru\n- **Tidak ada** pengecekan berdasarkan NIM dari email pattern\n\n## Masalah\n\nMahasiswa SIAKAD punya data di `members` tapi:\n- `email` kosong (belum diisi)\n- `member_id` = NIM (contoh: `432022413017`)\n\nKetika mahasiswa register/login dengan email kampus (misal `432022413017@student.unida.gontor.ac.id`):\n- Sistem tidak mengenali bahwa NIM `432022413017` sudah ada\n- Malah buat akun baru dengan `member_id` = `M20251228XXXX`\n\n## Konsep Solusi\n\n### Flow Deteksi Member SIAKAD\n\n```\nUser input email\n    ↓\nCek apakah email domain kampus UNIDA?\n    ↓ Ya\nExtract NIM dari email (bagian sebelum @)\n    ↓\nCek Member::where('member_id', $nim)->exists()?\n    ↓ Ya (Data SIAKAD ditemukan)\n    │\n    ├─ Jika email member kosong → Update email, link akun\n    │\n    └─ Jika email member berbeda → Konfirmasi/tolak\n    ↓ Tidak\nLanjut proses normal (buat baru atau error)\n```\n\n### Implementasi yang Dibutuhkan\n\n**1. Helper untuk extract NIM dari email kampus:**\n```php\nfunction extractNimFromEmail(string $email): ?string\n{\n    $campusDomains = [\n        'student.unida.gontor.ac.id',\n        'student.cs.unida.gontor.ac.id', \n        'student.iqt.unida.gontor.ac.id',\n        // dll\n    ];\n    \n    $domain = substr(strrchr($email, '@'), 1);\n    if (in_array($domain, $campusDomains)) {\n        return explode('@', $email)[0]; // NIM\n    }\n    return null;\n}\n```\n\n**2. Di Register.php - sebelum create:**\n```php\n// Cek apakah ada data SIAKAD dengan NIM dari email\n$nim = $this->extractNimFromEmail($this->email);\nif ($nim) {\n    $existingMember = Member::where('member_id', $nim)->first();\n    if ($existingMember) {\n        // Update member SIAKAD dengan data baru\n        $existingMember->update([\n            'email' => $this->email,\n            'phone' => $this->phone,\n            'password' => Hash::make($this->password),\n            'profile_completed' => true,\n        ]);\n        Auth::guard('member')->login($existingMember);\n        return redirect()->route('member.dashboard');\n    }\n}\n// Lanjut create baru jika tidak ketemu\n```\n\n**3. Di SocialAuthController - handleNormalLogin:**\n```php\n// Sebelum create member baru, cek NIM\n$nim = $this->extractNimFromEmail($googleUser->getEmail());\nif ($nim) {\n    $existingMember = Member::where('member_id', $nim)->first();\n    if ($existingMember) {\n        // Link Google ke member SIAKAD\n        $existingMember->update([\n            'email' => $googleUser->getEmail(),\n            'profile_completed' => true,\n        ]);\n        // Create social account link\n        SocialAccount::create([...]);\n        Auth::guard('member')->login($existingMember);\n        return redirect()->route('member.dashboard');\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## Pertanyaan Sebelum Implementasi\n\n1. **Domain email kampus apa saja?** (student.unida.gontor.ac.id, dll)\n2. **Apakah NIM selalu di bagian depan email?** (contoh: `432022413017@student...`)\n3. **Jika member SIAKAD sudah punya email berbeda, apa yang harus dilakukan?** (tolak / overwrite / konfirmasi)\n4. **Apakah perlu validasi tambahan?** (misal: nama harus mirip dengan data SIAKAD)\n\nMau saya implementasikan dengan asumsi standar, atau ada penyesuaian?\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "> Oke sudah bisa, apa yang terjadi barusan? saya sedikit panik.",
    "Tenang, website sudah kembali normal. Ini yang terjadi:\n\n## Kronologi Masalah\n\n1. **Saya mengubah permission .env menjadi 640** (`chmod 640 .env`)\n   - Tujuannya untuk keamanan (hanya owner & group yang bisa baca)\n   - **Masalah:** Web server (www-data) tidak bisa membaca file .env karena bukan owner/group\n\n2. **Akibatnya:** Laravel tidak bisa membaca APP_KEY dari .env → Error 500 \"No application encryption key\"\n\n3. **Solusi:** Kembalikan permission ke 644 (`chmod 644 .env`) + cache config\n   - 644 = owner bisa read/write, group & others bisa read\n   - Dengan `config:cache`, Laravel menyimpan semua config ke cache sehingga tidak perlu baca .env setiap request\n\n## Pelajaran\n\nPermission .env yang terlalu ketat (640) bisa menyebabkan web down jika web server berjalan sebagai user berbeda. Di server production dengan deployment seperti ini, **644 adalah permission yang aman** karena:\n- File .env sudah di luar public directory\n- Tidak bisa diakses via web\n- `config:cache` membuat Laravel tidak perlu baca .env langsung\n\n## Status Sekarang\n\n✅ Website berjalan normal\n✅ APP_DEBUG=false (aman)\n✅ Security middleware aktif\n✅ Config ter-cache\n\nMaaf sudah membuat panik! Ke depan saya akan lebih hati-hati dengan perubahan permission di production.\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "> Oke sudah berhasil semua, jelaskankenapa itu tadi, saya sedikit panik.",
    "Tenang, sudah solved! Ini penjelasannya:\n\n## Kronologi Masalah\n\n### 1. Root Cause: Duplicate Alpine.js\nSaat commit `3669296` (Fix Alpine.js not loading on static pages), ditambahkan:\n```html\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js\"></script>\n```\n\nPadahal **Livewire 3 sudah bundle Alpine.js** secara otomatis. Jadi ada 2 Alpine running → konflik → Livewire form submit tidak berfungsi.\n\n### 2. Kenapa Login Redirect Loop?\n- User klik tombol Login\n- `wire:submit=\"login\"` tidak bisa dipanggil karena Alpine/Livewire konflik\n- Form submit sebagai HTML biasa (bukan AJAX Livewire)\n- Server tidak proses login → redirect balik ke login page\n- Tidak ada error message karena Livewire tidak pernah handle request\n\n### 3. Kenapa Google OAuth Tetap Berfungsi (Awalnya)?\nGoogle OAuth pakai redirect URL biasa, tidak pakai Livewire. Jadi tidak terpengaruh konflik Alpine.\n\n### 4. Kenapa Google OAuth Ikut Rusak Kemudian?\nSaat saya ubah `SESSION_DOMAIN=library.unida.gontor.ac.id`, cookie session jadi tidak valid untuk browser yang sudah punya cookie lama dengan domain berbeda.\n\n## Fix yang Dilakukan\n\n1. **Hapus duplicate Alpine.js CDN** - Livewire sudah include Alpine\n2. **Hapus manual Livewire script** - Livewire auto-inject via `@livewireScripts`\n3. **Tambah `@livewireScripts`** - Memastikan Livewire JS ter-load\n4. **Kembalikan SESSION_DOMAIN=null**\n5. **Ubah SESSION_COOKIE name** - Force semua user dapat cookie baru, tidak perlu clear manual\n\n## Pelajaran\n- Jangan tambah Alpine.js CDN jika pakai Livewire 3\n- Hati-hati ubah session config di production\n- Test di lokal dulu sebelum deploy\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "Done! Emoji sudah diperbanyak dengan kategori: Wajah, Gestur, Simbol, Objek, dan Alam.\n\n---\n\n## Konsep Voice Note untuk Chat\n\n### Arsitektur yang Direkomendasikan\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n│   Browser       │     │   Laravel       │     │   Storage       │\n│   (MediaRecorder│────▶│   (Upload API)  │────▶│   (S3/Local)    │\n│   API)          │     │                 │     │                 │\n└─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Komponen Utama\n\n1. **Frontend (Recording)**\n   - Gunakan `MediaRecorder API` (native browser)\n   - Format: WebM/Opus (ukuran kecil, kualitas bagus)\n   - Max durasi: 60 detik (biar file tidak besar)\n\n2. **Backend (Storage)**\n   - Upload via Livewire `wire:model` atau AJAX\n   - Simpan di `storage/app/voice-notes/` atau S3\n   - Database: tambah kolom `voice_path` di tabel `chat_messages`\n\n3. **Auto-Delete (5 bulan)**\n   - Scheduled command: `php artisan voice:cleanup`\n   - Jalankan daily via cron\n   - Hapus file + update database\n\n### Estimasi Ukuran Storage\n\n| Durasi | Ukuran (WebM/Opus) |\n|--------|-------------------|\n| 30 detik | ~50-100 KB |\n| 60 detik | ~100-200 KB |\n\nJika 100 voice note/hari × 30 hari × 5 bulan = **~7.5 GB max**\n\n### Implementasi Minimal\n\n```php\n// Migration\nSchema::table('chat_messages', function ($table) {\n    $table->string('voice_path')->nullable();\n    $table->integer('voice_duration')->nullable(); // detik\n});\n\n// Model\nprotected $casts = ['voice_duration' => 'integer'];\n\n// Cleanup Command (daily cron)\nChatMessage::whereNotNull('voice_path')\n    ->where('created_at', '<', now()->subMonths(5))\n    ->each(fn($m) => Storage::delete($m->voice_path) && $m->update(['voice_path' => null]));\n```\n\n### Browser Support\n- Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari (iOS 14.3+) ✅\n- IE ❌ (tidak masalah)\n\n### Pertimbangan\n\n| Pro | Kontra |\n|-----|--------|\n| UX lebih baik | Storage bertambah |\n| Komunikasi lebih cepat | Perlu handle permission mic |\n| Modern feature | Tidak bisa di-search |\n\n### Rekomendasi\n\n**Ya, bisa diimplementasikan** dengan effort sedang (~1-2 hari kerja). Arsitektur:\n- Local storage dulu (hemat biaya)\n- Limit 60 detik per voice\n- Auto-cleanup 5 bulan via cron\n- Fallback text jika browser tidak support\n\nMau saya implementasikan?\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "Selamat pagi! Konsep yang bagus untuk menjangkau mahasiswa yang tidak punya akses WhatsApp/Telegram.\n\n## Konsep Member Chat System\n\n### Arsitektur yang Direkomendasikan: **Gabung dengan Staff Chat**\n\nAlasan:\n1. **Satu inbox untuk staff** - tidak perlu buka 2 tempat berbeda\n2. **Reuse infrastruktur** - tabel `chat_rooms`, `chat_messages` sudah ada\n3. **Konsisten** - notifikasi,
